Love Messages App Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 2/8/2024

1. Introduction
Welcome to the Love Messages app. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled safely and responsibly. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information, including device identifiers.

2. Information We Collect
a. Device Information
To improve app functionality, we may collect certain device information, including:

Android ID
Serial Number (SN)
We collect this information only after obtaining your explicit consent.

b. Personal Information
We do not collect personally identifiable information (such as your name, email address, or phone number) unless you provide it voluntarily.

3. How We Use Your Information
Device Identifiers: We may use Android ID and serial numbers to support app functionality and improve user experience. We collect this data strictly with user consent and only use it as permitted by applicable privacy laws and regulations.
4. User Consent
Upon installation and before using our app, users are prompted to review and accept our Privacy Policy. By consenting, you agree to our collection of the device identifiers listed above. You may withdraw your consent at any time via the app’s settings.

5. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no system is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute data security.

6. Third-Party Services
Our app may include links to third-party services or use third-party APIs. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party services. Please review their privacy policies before using their services.

7. Data Retention
We retain your information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.

8. Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for use by children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected such information, we will take steps to delete it.

9. Privacy Tag
Our app complies with the privacy tag requirements specified by AppGallery. The collection of device identifiers (Android ID and Serial Number) is transparently disclosed in the app’s Privacy Tag within AppGallery Connect.

10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted in the app and will take effect immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

11. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:

Email: gkyando@gmail.com
Phone: +255678733827

12. Consent
By using our app, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

